# Trivy ignore file
# Documented exceptions for the parkhub-rust monorepo. Each entry must
# carry an explicit justification — review on every workflow refresh.

# KSV-0109: "ConfigMap stores secrets in key MODULE_PARKING_PASS"
# False positive — `MODULE_PARKING_PASS` is a boolean feature flag for the
# Parking Pass module (helm/parkhub/values.yaml: `parkingPass: true`), not
# a credential. Trivy's secret heuristic matches the substring "PASS".
KSV-0109
